            "paragraph_text_size": 17,
            "paragraph_text_color": "#0f0f0f",
            "paragraph_1_enabled": true,
            "paragraph_1_title": "",
            "paragraph_1_text": "<p><strong>We believe</strong> the greatest impact comes from an internal overflow, not an external grind.</p><p></p>",
            "paragraph_2_enabled": true,
            "paragraph_2_title": "",
            "paragraph_2_text": "<p><strong>We believe</strong> conventional leadership has it backward, demanding you sacrifice your peace to amplify your success.</p>",
            "paragraph_3_enabled": true,
            "paragraph_3_title": "",
            "paragraph_3_text": "<p><strong>We exist</strong> to quiet the noise, allowing you to find your center and remember who you are.</p>",
            "paragraph_4_enabled": true,
            "paragraph_4_title": "",
            "paragraph_4_text": "<p><strong>We know</strong> that true elevation—emotionally, mentally, and spiritually—requires both sacred space and guided revelation. Through deeply personal, guided conversations with founder Nancy Vuu, we walk with you into your highest state of being.</p>",
            "paragraph_5_enabled": true,
            "paragraph_5_title": "",
            "paragraph_5_text": "<p><strong>We offer</strong> a safe haven to dream again—because a lasting, sovereign legacy can only be built from a place of profound rest, restored identity, and renewed purpose.</p>"
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
