          "type": "dimension",
          "settings": {
            "number": "01",
            "heading": "THE SANCTUARY OF STILLNESS",
            "subtitle": "Nervous System Restoration & Luxury Care",
            "text": "Recalibrate your body and mind through the curated silence of our majestic mountain haven. We transition you from the exhaustion of high-stakes leadership and continuous output into a state of profound, effortless peace through luxury care and bespoke nourishment."
