            "heading": "Silencing the Noise",
            "subtitle": "Releasing Expectations & Finding Clarity",
            "text": "Detach from the overwhelming logistics of daily demands. Through guided conversations in our sacred space, we help you release the heavy echo of generic ambition, allowing you to finally quiet the noise, find your center, and hear your own voice again."
          }
        },
        "d3": {
          "type": "dimension",
