            "heading": "ANCHORING THE IDENTITY",
            "subtitle": "Restoring True Identity & Intrinsic Worth",
            "text": "Reclaim your unshakeable intrinsic worth. We guide you to gently strip away the layers of who the world expects you to be, firmly anchoring your true identity and the belief that you are fashioned for love and greatness in this next chapter."
          }
        },
