            "description": "<p>This exquisite immersion moves you out of the high-stakes \"Boardroom\" energy and into the creative freedom of the \"Atelier.\" Designed exclusively for the woman at the helm who has already \"arrived,\" this sanctuary is a place to remember how to play, dream, and belong. Here, the heavy \"Weight of the Crown\" is beautifully replaced by your true \"Mantle of Authority and Presence.\"</p><p>It is a four-day celebration of high-level sisterhood, strategic alignment, and the unapologetic freedom to dream even bigger. Surrounded by a circle of peers who speak your language and celebrate your magnitude, you will find the elusive white space your calendar usually denies you. We do not just network; we fiercely champion each other’s upcoming big moves.</p><p>The definitive highlight of this sanctuary is the literal \"Couture of the Self.\" In a series of collaborative design labs, you will work directly with Nancy Vuu to architect your own Bespoke Wardrobe. You will co-design the masterful garments that reflect your current power and your future destiny—pieces that tell the world exactly who you are before you ever speak a word.</p>",
