            "modal_trigger": true
          }
        },
        "destination_6RWhJz": {
          "type": "destination",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/10.jpg",
            "quota": "",
            "location": "Kaneohe, HI & Napa Valley, Ca",
            "title": "THE DREAMS REALIZED IMMERSION: The Architecture of Implementation",
            "description": "While DREAM Again Restores the Dreamer, DREAMS REALIZED Equips the Architect.\n\nThe DREAMS REALIZED Immersion is the definitive, high-level next step for the global visionary ready to move from internal recalibration to External Sovereignty. Located within a private sanctuary of quiet serenity, this 4-day, 3-night intensive focuses exclusively on the \"How\"—the technical engineering required to translate your strategic internal overflow into a visible, lived reality. We are not discussing \"inspiration\"; we are implementing Infrastructure Redemption.\n\nThrough private strategic consultation and the deployment of the Nancy Vuu Blueprint of Honor, you will bridge the gap between divine inspiration and industrial distinction. Discover the concrete mechanics required to engineered the intersection of honor, visibility, and restorative ethics into your personal life and business legacy. Nancy Vuu provides the specialized structural guidance needed to manifest your vision across your entire organization’s DNA.\n\nThis is a workspace where strategic architecture meets legacy-building. You will not leave with a \"dream\"; you will leave with a Sovereign Roadmap to Fulfillment and the unshakeable Mantle of Authority required to lead your next era. Enjoy total, curated Sovereign Alignment with all-inclusive amenities: bespoke cuisine, exquisitely tailored strategic activities, rustic lodging, and curated giftings, including specialized transport to and from the retreat sanctuary. Build your legacy from bedrock.",
